Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说人类上月球？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.90,0:01:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.43,0:01:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好饱 吃得好饱\N三顿都吃牛肉火锅也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.60,0:02:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是谁在付帐的\N还是“红牛”的牛肉火锅最棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.81,0:02:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外国已经在做这方面的研究了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.75,0:02:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把人放进这么大的大炮\N对准月亮发射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.66,0:02:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过\N这个需要很多复杂的计算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.43,0:02:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是希望你能做做\N吃霞气让肚子饱的研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是可结出黄金的树种子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 你干嘛听他胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事连小孩子都不会相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.49,0:02:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的绝不是凭空幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.42,0:02:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科学发达的话\N人类一定会去月球的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也想去月亮看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.43,0:03:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N你听我说这件事没有嘲笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎 要回去了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…\N能够去月球真的很不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你笨笨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲话很刻薄耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他的东西 他忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.09,0:03:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七十九话\N胜海舟与剑心\N活在幕末时代的二人的宿缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.78,0:03:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你忘记这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.52,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才离开没多久\N东京就变得这么危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.26,0:04:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰 你保护这两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的东西 你振作点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她比你还可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁马！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.35,0:05:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你是谁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想拿老师的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.66,0:05:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大久保铁马\N就来当你的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情才刚要变有趣呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你没受伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.31,0:05:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 是这些人救我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们拔刀相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.15,0:05:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里\N正好当饭后运动是不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.15,0:05:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.75,0:05:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我不是跟您说过\N别轻易外出的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是有这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师若是有个万一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我送您到大屋去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎 你陪在旁边\N居然没尽到保护老师之责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.31,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 我已经受不了你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.28,0:06:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.29,0:06:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在今后一肩挑起日本的人\N却连剑术都学不好 丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我不要这种徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 干嘛说成这样呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 那有这么轻易就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们自己的问题\N请你们别插口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.47,0:06:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是你们认为这个\N满口梦话的小子能让人寄望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这种事不试试怎知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.88,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为神谷活心流剑术师父\N我神谷薰一定可以把他教好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看是白费力气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎 在你剑术没练好之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.83,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准再来登入我的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 铁马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.94,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫做什么 我问你名字呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.85,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫胜海舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.44,0:07:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没完没完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.78,0:07:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太沮丧了 你是男子汉\N应该让他们刮目相看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用啦 没用啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.38,0:07:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要是有那个志气\N就不会被逐出门墙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.72,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过份哦\N不管那师父有多了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这样\N一句话就把徒弟赶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.16,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的有待权商\N胜海舟不是那种冷血老人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.96,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜海舟不是幕末时代\N支撑幕府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护江户\N面对逼近的萨长大军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做下“不流血开城”\N决定的男人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是通达荷兰学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.28,0:08:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还跟遗美使节同行\N看穿时代潮流的聪明人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.48,0:08:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位老人会在明治治世之时\N叫他学剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想都很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管他以前是怎样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现况是大五郎无家可归
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里修行可以变得很强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.86,0:08:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼死练习一定有转机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那刻薄的老人！吓一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.87,0:08:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对哦 我变强的话\N老师就会承认我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SCIENCE是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.98,0:08:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科学啊\N西方专做研究的一门学问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.02,0:09:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师说那是\N今后的日本需要的知识…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有铁马那样的徒弟的话\N老师才会有尊严吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.63,0:09:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁马是那位拿着怪剑\N的很神气的家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.80,0:09:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫西洋剑\N是西方剑术所用的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.74,0:09:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是铁马留学英国时学会的\N他的剑术很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.68,0:09:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且年纪轻轻就前途无量\N当上政府的高级官僚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样是徒弟 我却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.46,0:09:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你对科学比较了解吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.46,0:09:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就就是有样东西\N不输给那家伙了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.04,0:09:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有科学的话\N就可以上去月球吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.24,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里 你看这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.31,0:09:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把人放进弹丸里面\N再放进大炮对准月球发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.78,0:10:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是法国朱斯贝伦写的书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻成日文的话\N应该叫做月世界之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.47,0:10:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 大清早吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还问我干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.37,0:10:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎一直没有回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 等他剑术练好再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.78,0:10:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎根本不适合学剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.78,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你也这么说过不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢做学问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好钻研\N将来一定可以成为大人物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有说过那句话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我去那个道场\N迎接大五郎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你阻止也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.93,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你要是不听我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你也不用回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 这个不明理的糊涂老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 你这么急要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.96,0:11:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了\N我要去道场迎接大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.46,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 铁马\N你这么早来有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.03,0:11:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来探望老师情况的\N我很在意昨天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心爸爸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.61,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…让我送你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.98,0:11:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上班的途中\N曾经过那个道场附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 就麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.64,0:12:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.14,0:12:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎今天起\N就是神谷活心流的门生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.11,0:12:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等于是我的师弟了\N以后多多指教了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也请你多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么首先\N你去打扫道场的地板吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也得动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么我也得擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦 这也是修行之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 他学得成吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.67,0:12:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有阿薰在教\N没问题 没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.49,0:12:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你很好的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.56,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逸子是来迎接大五郎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说\N那个顽固老头原谅他了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说的话你别太在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.01,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.68,0:13:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师叫我学剑术\N一定是为我好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人有适合他的事\N也有不适合他的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不适合学剑术的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还有学问不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会替你向爸爸说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.53,0:13:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下\N大五郎是我的门生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你随便带回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎是我们的书生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.78,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是被赶出来的\N被你们那不明理的老人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来接人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩别吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你闭上嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.02,0:13:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧\N大五郎都说想留在这儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁马！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐不必那么在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为胜家的书生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为老师的眼光是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.10,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有把老师的教诲\N发扬光大的能力与气概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早点死心对大五郎也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.21,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在这种道场实在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 失礼了\N我只是认为在这里修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不会让他功夫进步多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许这最适合大五郎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.93,0:14:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还让这种小姐当师父…呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.23,0:14:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么讲\N就让你见识神谷活心流的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.30,0:14:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我学的也是剑术\N不过是西方的西洋剑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.71,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁马 不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.28,0:14:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我只是让那位小姐\N见识世界的现实罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你让开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是高手哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.06,0:15:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种新时代\N还玩弄那种木棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放肆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.88,0:15:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以打架呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我得赶快上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.89,0:15:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 我要先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去时请小心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.47,0:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我要暂时留在这里修行\N请你转告老师吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.58,0:16:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 既然你心意已决\N我也不再多说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我是不会离开这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.66,0:16:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大五郎剑术进步以前\N我要留在这里受你们照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？当然是准备晚餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.95,0:16:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在这里看大五郎修行\N至少让我做点事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.92,0:16:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.69,0:16:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.72,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她做的比小姐的好吃太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.56,0:16:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是实话 没办法嘛 丑女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.53,0:16:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.10,0:17:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰是个很严格的人\N虽然看起来不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也常挨她的骂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.74,0:17:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 大五郎你真喜欢读书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有这个长处嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.93,0:17:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逸子小姐果然还是\N适合铁马那样的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.01,0:17:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 不管我多努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.88,0:17:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都无法像铁马那样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们同样是老师的学生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.75,0:17:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是逸子不顾父亲反对\N担心你 来这里了不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.58,0:18:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这时候你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去通知他逸子住这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去爸爸那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦 反正又不担心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 擅自上门打扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.36,0:19:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这么大的屋子里\N只有我一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.27,0:19:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逸子跟大五郎都在神谷道场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 蒙你们照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子个性很泼辣\N没给你们添麻烦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.18,0:19:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的手艺好\N大家吃得非常高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多安静啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样独处 不禁想起过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.44,0:19:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有过这样子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我想也想不到\N自己会有这样的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因这过去我太出名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.55,0:20:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要我的命的刺客相当的多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.16,0:20:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是开国 又是尊王攘夷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.23,0:20:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时\N大家都为自己的理想赌命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今回想那个时代真是热烈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么时候\N我看到了未来的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.44,0:20:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想身为活在那个时代的人\N我多少尽到一些责任了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给年轻人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.85,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.92,0:21:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这话题很沉闷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.19,0:21:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当做一个老人在罗嗦废话\N把它忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.32,0:21:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜先生\N你是不是隐瞒了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逸子和大五郎就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.84,0:21:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 现在该叫你绯村剑心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.72,0:21:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会照顾他们的 告辞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜先生是故意\N把大五郎与逸子调远的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.44,0:22:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一个人不知道\N想要应付什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.46,0:22:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们光明正大的走出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天的那批人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.17,0:22:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准你再接近胜海舟了
